burn((uint256,uint256,address,address,ui.details: Burn short position. Withdraw token0, when long token0 is burnt. Withdraw token1, when long token1 is burnt.Can only be called before the maturity of the pool.

params.param: The parameters for the burn function.

returns.token0AndLong0Amount: The amount of token0 withdrawn and long0 burnt.
returns.token1AndLong1Amount: The amount of token1 withdrawn and long1 burnt.

collect((uint256,uint256,address,address.details: Burn short position, withdraw token0 and token1.Can only be called after the maturity of the pool.

params.param: The parameters for the collect function.

getByIndex(uint256).details: Get the strike and maturity of the option in the option enumeration list.

mint((uint256,uint256,address,address,ad.details: Mint position. Mint long token0 position when token0 is deposited. Mint long token1 position when token1 is deposited.Can only be called before the maturity of the pool.

params.param: The parameters for the mint function.

returns.token0AndLong0Amount: The amount of token0 deposited and long0 minted.
returns.token1AndLong1Amount: The amount of token1 deposited and long1 minted.

optionFactory().details: Returns the factory address that deployed this contract.

positionOf(uint256,uint256,address,uint8.details: Returns the position of an owner of the option.

params.owner: The address of the owner of the position.
params.position: The type of position inquired. More information in the Position module.
params.strike: The strike ratio of token1 per token0 of the position.

swap((uint256,uint256,address,address,bo.details: If the direction is from long token0 to long token1, burn long token0 and mint equivalent long token1, also deposit token1 and withdraw token0. If the direction is from long token1 to long token0, burn long token1 and mint equivalent long token0, also deposit token0 and withdraw token1.Can only be called before the maturity of the pool.

params.param: The parameters for the swap function.

returns.token0AndLong0Amount: If direction is Long0ToLong1, the amount of token0 withdrawn and long0 burnt. If direction is Long1ToLong0, the amount of token0 deposited and long0 minted.
returns.token1AndLong1Amount: If direction is Long0ToLong1, the amount of token1 deposited and long1 minted. If direction is Long1ToLong0, the amount of token1 withdrawn and long1 burnt.

token0().details: Returns the first ERC20 token address of the pair.

token1().details: Returns the second ERC20 token address of the pair.

totalPosition(uint256,uint256,uint8).details: Returns the total position of the option.

params.position: The type of position inquired. More information in the Position module.
params.strike: The strike ratio of token1 per token0 of the position.

params.position: The type of position transferred. More information in the Position module.
params.strike: The strike ratio of token1 per token0 of the position.
params.to: The address of the receipient of the position.
